#: table_sizing.xhp#par_id3146497.help.text
#, fuzzy
msgid "You can also distribute rows and columns evenly using the icons on the <item type=\"menuitem\">Optimize</item> toolbar on the <item type=\"menuitem\">Table</item> Bar."
